{"tid":60643,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"笑死笨柒之2016十大笑爆黃洋達事件～","createTime":"2016-12-30T15:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T15:01:43.000Z","uid":31748,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d80f33d92f28e7fbffd7f9546bae1842789602e","tid":60643,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/9yoSD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2F9yoSD.jpg&h=3e989c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【2016十大笑爆黃洋達事件】<br />\n<br />\n第十位：用YouTube做直播，在線人數即刻現形少十倍。<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrleung.com/iii/14770582859397.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrleung.com%2Fiii%2F14770582859397.png&h=02eee2ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"http://mrleung.com/iii/14770583762804.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrleung.com%2Fiii%2F14770583762804.png&h=36e2c976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"http://mrleung.com/iii/14770584903686.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrleung.com%2Fiii%2F14770584903686.png&h=604e80f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n支持大亨！<br />\r\n《笑死笨柒》宜家有6464<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（686<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</span></span>名觀眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n686 / 6464 =0.10612623762<br />\r\n冇可能架！<br />\r\n實際人數得十分一？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\nYOUTUBE高層你一定係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收撚左錢搞真心救港嘅熱普城fuck</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrleung.com/iii/14770588937662.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrleung.com%2Fiii%2F14770588937662.png&h=c17465c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"http://mrleung.com/iii/14770590337214.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrleung.com%2Fiii%2F14770590337214.png&h=da6c020b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n我們的教主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第九位：以衝擊中聯辦係ON9行為去解釋熱時零報導。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/MvE2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2FMvE2S.jpg&h=ef35ece7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第八位：熱時年宵攤位拍烏蠅，隔離100毛就大排長龍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r8-PASO0-rU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr8-PASO0-rU&d=RsxxxD658N3gi6tisN0bb2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=55b1687a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r8-PASO0-rU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/09uih.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2F09uih.jpg&h=5033936c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第七位：懶理柏洋入獄，黃洋達夫婦笠垃圾袋遊山玩水。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sXgpI5jYCOc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsXgpI5jYCOc&d=RsxxxD658N3gi6tisN0bb2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=1e743d2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sXgpI5jYCOc</a><br />\n<br />\n第六位：張德江到港，為掩飾怕死，黃洋達話唔L理佢。<br />\n<br />\n第五位：驚冇得選，搶簽確認書，點知民主派個個唔簽。<br />\n<br />\n第四位：安全才出動，黃洋達率眾去日領抗議任天堂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/FbS0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2FFbS0B.jpg&h=34df173c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三位：被多人秒殺，黃洋達選舉論壇醜態百出。<br />\n<br />\n第二位：黃洋達台灣示範勇武燒中國旗。<br />\n<br />\n第一位：立法會兩連敗，黃洋達一路走來，始終唔得，廢過廢陶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/RIlfC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2FRIlfC.jpg&h=ca6628fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/YODHV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2FYODHV.jpg&h=71a363ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/EDUdi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2FEDUdi.jpg&h=abd49e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=-oacw_Vi_14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-oacw_Vi_14&d=RsxxxD658N3gi6tisN0bb2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=237ee539\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=-oacw_Vi_14</a><br />\n<br />\n2014年<br />\r\n<br />\r\n黃洋達：唔該你唔好咁侮辱我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n\r<br />\n陳秀慧：做咗議員就好似陳志全咁㗎啦！<br />\r<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n\r<br />\n黃洋達：oh so sad<br />\r<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n\r<br />\n\r<br />\n\r<br />\n\r<br />\n\r<br />\n\r<br />\n2016宣佈參選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3911b48d7535de272555c6ea1474ed6f08aac0c9","tid":60643,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf776da2651c793624f60b927c0fe6e7eac8bf6c","tid":60643,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053b1eba70cee4180a657e4bc29259d58c16dc93","tid":60643,"uid":67558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"呢個仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5717ffcc6521c15de7fbff179069c22052646c75","tid":60643,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor